{"tid":2007831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上午驅逐記者 下午邀訪工廠","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T14:39:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"abb1e2cebeda0e8f607cae2c026dfe78b85e7489","tid":2007831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/2VTBC5OX3QTSNIKHPEB2HJYYKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F2VTBC5OX3QTSNIKHPEB2HJYYKE%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=1fbd133c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2F2VTBC5OX3QTSNIKHPEB2HJYYKE%2F&h=a82188d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/2VTBC5OX3QTSNIKHPEB2HJYYKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n上午驅逐記者 下午邀訪工廠<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多家傳媒昨早到有份生產的荃灣南豐紗廠查詢，被紗廠負責人驅趕，「關於Cu Masks你哋問返創科局啦！」至下午獲政府委託統籌計劃的香港紡織及成衣研發中心（HKRITA），突邀傳媒到大埔工業村龍達環保紗廠了解口罩消毒及包裝。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高官倘誤導公眾屬行為失當<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870103_95fb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870103_95fb.gif&h=c8fd338e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳媒昨到南豐紗廠採訪口罩生產，遭職員要求離開。<br />\n<br />\nHKRITA總監（業務拓展）陳慧欣昨稱，計劃生產約900萬個口罩，其中850萬個由晶苑集團的越南廠房生產，已完成500萬個並。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870102_2677.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870102_2677.gif&h=a5927edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳媒昨獲安排參觀龍達環保紗廠的加工程序。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在港臭氧消毒包裝<br />\n<br />\n口罩經臭氧消毒儀器消毒約1小時，再運往無塵室包裝，工人穿全副保護衣、戴口罩、穿鞋套，量度體溫及消毒後，才可進。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳慧欣指，2月與政府洽商後即聯絡廠商，最終如何決定由誰生產，她僅。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙"}]}